If you dont know who Desi Perkins is youre seriously missing out and should search her on YouTube right this instant PERIOD

Perkins is a goddess made famous for her dashing fashion sense flawless application of makeup and her allaround perfect life PERIOD

If you follow her on Instagram theres no doubt youll see she is always modeling and promoting Quay Australia PERIOD This sunglasses brand could quite possibly change your life PERIOD

If you go to their website you can shop a vast variety of different shapes and sizes of sunglasses but the most popular item is the Quay X Desi Perkins High Key aviators PERIOD

The collection launched in June of  and this style of sunglasses sells out almost every single time it drops so you know it has got be good PERIOD

If you look up product reviews of this brand so many people swear by it PERIOD Perkins helped make Quay a huge name but celebrities like the Kardashians the Hadids and Jennifer Lopez are always stepping out in this brand as well PERIOD

There are many other designs to choose from besides just Perkins style but if you want that kind specifically youll have to keep your eyes peeled for when they get restocked PERIOD

The highdemand aviators feature oversized mirrored lenses metal frames a double bridge adjustable nose pads and are offered in black gold and blue PERIOD

On QuayAustralia.com you can even view pictures buyers uploaded of themselves wearing the glasses and how great the shape looks on so many different faces PERIOD

This particular style rings in at  but they are well worth the money PERIOD They look just as good as RayBans or any other highend name brand and are half the cost PERIOD

So if youre looking for a good pair of sunglasses that wont break the bank or break in general shop Quay Australia PERIOD You will not be disappointed PERIOD
